You have a custom ROM installed. Custom ROMs can cause problems with AK47 Messenger and are unsupported by our customer service team.

Custom ROMs have been known to cause problems with keyboard input methods, cloud to device (C2DM) notifications as well as timely and accurate message delivery. Further, many custom ROMs are bundled with task killing properties that cause the same problems as a 3rd party task killer. Please understand that custom ROMs are not supported by %s and that you use them at your own risk.
